Package com.earth2me.essentials.register.payment

Class Methods

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.earth2me.essentials.register.payment.Methods
  • public final class Methods
extends Object
    The Methods initializes Methods that utilize the Method interface based on a "first come, first served" basis.

    Allowing you to check whether a payment method exists or not.

    Methods also allows you to set a preferred method of payment before it captures payment plugins in the initialization process.

    in bukkit.yml: 

      economy:
      preferred: "iConomy"
